<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM5.7">
<l>poṅkiya pāṟkaṭaṟ paḷḷikoḷ vāṉaip puṇarvatō rācaiyi ṉāleṉ</l>
<l>koṅkai kiḷarntu kumaittuk kutukalit tāviyai yākulañ ceyyum</l>
<l>aṅkuyi lēyuṉak keṉṉa maṟaintuṟai vāḻiyuñ caṅkumoṇ ṭaṇṭun</l>
<l>taṅkiya kaiyava ṉaivarak kūvilnī cālat tarumam peṟuti.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Out of the desire to unite with Him who sleeps on the foaming and raging milk ocean,</l>
<l>my breasts cause grief to [my] life[breath] by springing up, afflicting [me],</l>
<l rend="indent">and being in a rapture.</l>
<l>O beautiful koel! What does living in hiding [bring] you?</l>
<l>If you cry in such a way that He whose hands bear a discus, a conch, and a bright club</l>
<l rend="indent">comes, you will get plenty of merits!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
